#  Streamlit Cloud Secrets Template
#
#  When deploying to Streamlit Cloud:
#    1. Go to your app dashboard → Settings → Secrets
#    2. Paste ONLY the key=value pairs (not this comment block)
#    3. The app reads them via  os.environ  or  st.secrets
#
#  For local development, use .env instead (see .env.example).
